###  http://mmoon.org/core/Lexeme
mmoon:Lexeme rdf:type owl:Class ;
             rdfs:subClassOf mmoon:LexicalEntry ;
             mmoon:definition "A lexeme [lexema] is a word in its capacity as a unit of the lexicon. In a text, it appears in form of diverse word forms. [Christian Lehmann, under \"lexeme\" at http://linguistik.uni-regensburg.de:8080/lido/Lido]"@en ;
